{"tid":2061031,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「學術討論」 香港人應學習《義勇軍進行曲》","createTime":"2020-06-12T05:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T06:02:44.000Z","uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1de38ba19709a9d67821c721efae5da7f29278f5","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋班連登仔好心學下唱《義勇軍進行曲》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起來！不願做奴隸的人們！（起身啦！唔想做港奴的人們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！（我地要不惜血肉，要建立<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新嘅</span></strong></span>長城）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中華民族到了最危險的時候，（中華民族依家到咗最危險嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每個人被迫着發出最後的吼聲。（咁慘烈 去到最後 迫住叫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n起來！起來！起來！（起身啦）<br />\n<br />\n我們萬眾一心，（我哋萬眾一心，一個共同目標）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（敵人有炮火都要前進啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n冒着敵人的炮火，前進！（繼續向前）<br />\n<br />\n前進！前進！進！（一定要向前進，唔好退，唔好走）"},{"pid":"25268a18794604170b8377e3804362d90be70ed4","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bb9da82e7031d05a8b921c42eeabd8a1ddace4","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"歌詞 唔可以改<br />\n絕不可以故意侮辱國歌"},{"pid":"541ea90730bc5969f9939ad4c75b3a99ee7f0414","tid":2061031,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"畢嬲都覺得国歌反撚到仆街<br />\n都唔知係咪小學雞唔識睇內容以為係打飛機愛国歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df900cb0d5725fa6fac6b27413f6b472cc4ee8c0","tid":2061031,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"唔洗改歌詞都夠哂反動"},{"pid":"84bb83c34dc6e56b6b7d16887c94f27de958685d","tid":2061031,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48bb9da82e7031d05a8b921c42eeabd8a1ddace4","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"歌詞 唔可以改<br />\n絕不可以故意侮辱國歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"唔洗改歌詞都夠哂反動"},{"pid":"1555fce5fb08d63d991179de5afc2a04477f947f","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"541ea90730bc5969f9939ad4c75b3a99ee7f0414","tid":2061031,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:52:47.000Z","msg":"畢嬲都覺得国歌反撚到仆街<br />\n都唔知係咪小學雞唔識睇內容以為係打飛機愛国歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"唔好改國歌<br />\n一定要唱 認真投入唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94966783b60c118bb41c392cf03414274e1a372c","tid":2061031,"uid":186,"like":0